Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.46,0:03:01.63,Drifters Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1617.6,255.9)\fad(420,500)}步声鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.46,0:03:01.63,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(1663.2,135.9)\fad(420,500)}第二幕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.50,0:03:05.55,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个 我明明都那么强调过了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.92,0:03:07.38,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你们居然还去废城
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.80,0:03:10.93,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我都那样说过了 不要和漂流者扯上关系
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.14,0:03:14.31,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,进入森林 去废城
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.39,0:03:16.23,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,还有和漂流者扯上关系
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.43,0:03:19.02,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,如果被领主发现的话可是要没命的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.19,0:03:21.27,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但那个漂流者濒死在路上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.27,0:03:22.06,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,没有但是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.61,0:03:26.28,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了 不要和他们扯上关系 懂了么 你们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.78,0:03:34.16,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 收获前吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.74,0:03:36.58,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.63,0:03:48.13,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,注意到了么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.55,0:03:49.38,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.26,0:03:52.51,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这股气息是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.60,0:03:55.52,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是交战的气息吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.27,0:04:02.10,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是火
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.27,0:04:05.27,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那些精灵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.94,0:04:12.74,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,被山贼或流寇袭击的交战的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.95,0:04:14.12,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,精灵是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.58,0:04:17.75,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是在森林的另一边生活着的奇怪的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.16,0:04:22.17,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那些 把你搬到这里的长耳朵…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.17,0:04:23.71,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.75,0:04:27.13,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 慢着 你想过去么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.13,0:04:29.97,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是哪里 会发生些什么 我都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.97,0:04:32.55,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这到底是梦还是现实 我也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.76,0:04:36.31,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我就只知道冲在最前线
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.43,0:04:42.23,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙是个蠢货啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.56,0:04:44.98,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才明明还一副快要死的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.69,0:04:48.07,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙是铁炮弹之类的东西做的么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.11,0:04:53.74,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他们会行动么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.82,0:04:55.83,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.62,0:04:58.83,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办 会变成怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.29,0:05:08.46,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,太慢了 太慢了 织田信长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.59,0:05:11.80,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 怎么了 第六天魔王
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.22,0:05:15.85,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,烦死了 我可是已经50岁的人了 蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.05,0:05:18.47,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,丰久阁下 请问你年纪多大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.85,0:05:19.81,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,三十
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.35,0:05:27.48,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 居然一副赢了的得意样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.65,0:05:31.19,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙和源平军记所记载的完全不同啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.16,0:05:41.79,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,救 救救我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.81,0:06:01.81,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,哟 小鬼们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.57,0:06:17.37,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,把头颅留下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.37,0:06:20.70,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是什么东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.74,0:06:23.00,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是废城的 漂流者么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.50,0:06:25.29,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我听不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.50,0:06:28.38,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么我完全听不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.50,0:06:30.71,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,说日语啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.13,0:06:37.55,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不会说日语的话 就去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.52,0:06:52.32,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,还真是奇怪的耳朵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.32,0:06:59.37,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就是你们帮我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.66,0:07:02.08,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这次到我还礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.37,0:07:06.79,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那些家伙就可以放过么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.79,0:07:10.96,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那些家伙也是不会说日语的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.04,0:07:13.30,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不是该死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.22,0:07:17.55,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.68,0:07:18.84,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 跟着我重复
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.01,0:07:20.22,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.18,0:07:24.56,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 说啊 救救我 救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.60,0:07:27.77,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,救救我 救救我 救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.14,0:07:31.69,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,好 就这么解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.06,0:07:34.03,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,好猛的逼迫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.32,0:07:37.57,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,见识到了能和一向众媲美的夸张说辞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.32,0:07:37.57,Difters PS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(360,17.4)}一向众：日本佛教宗派一向宗的信徒。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.62,0:07:47.71,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,装备太过齐全了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.33,0:07:51.21,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这些人可不是流寇或山贼之类的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.71,0:07:55.59,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,正规的士兵 是这里领主的士兵吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.71,0:07:58.01,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.97,0:08:01.72,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就好像在说「尽情来抢吧」的样子一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.39,0:08:11.48,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 那就去把村庄给拿下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.48,0:08:14.86,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,拿下？他们说了拿下么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.07,0:08:15.82,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.36,0:08:19.15,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,既不是挽救亦不是帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.40,0:08:20.45,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,而是拿下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.24,0:08:23.66,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他们天生就带着这样的「病」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.20,0:08:26.62,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是他们所具备的最强的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.74,0:08:29.87,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不 除此之外他们一无所有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.25,0:08:36.09,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他们的行动准则无论何时何地只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.76,0:08:40.38,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他们要开始征服国家了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.18,0:08:46.10,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,排列好队伍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.85,0:08:56.52,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这到底是怎么回事 阿拉姆大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.57,0:08:59.15,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我们到底犯了什么错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.40,0:09:01.70,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,村长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.40,0:09:06.95,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你们进入森林帮助了漂流物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.79,0:09:12.25,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,精灵进入森林 制弓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.41,0:09:14.67,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,还有与漂流者有瓜葛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.42,0:09:17.59,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,无论哪一件都是大罪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.88,0:09:22.72,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那是孩子们为了救助濒死的漂流者才这样做的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.76,0:09:25.93,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是小孩所以就要我们放过他们么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.97,0:09:28.64,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真是肤浅而厚颜无耻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.72,0:09:30.14,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这些精灵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.60,0:09:32.48,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,漂流物的管理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.60,0:09:35.44,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,全是由十月机关的魔术师们负责的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.60,0:09:38.40,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这些亚人种与其扯上关系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.48,0:09:40.61,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就应当问罪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.07,0:09:43.40,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你们难道认为没有暴露么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.74,0:09:45.03,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.07,0:09:47.12,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不讲道理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.12,0:09:48.99,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不进入森林的话 无论木柴还是果实
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.99,0:09:51.45,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,都无法获得 也无法进行狩猎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.75,0:09:54.12,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不仅逼迫我们做从未做过的农奴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.25,0:09:56.50,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,还把村里的女性都带走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.67,0:10:01.76,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,现在孩子们居然因为帮助濒死的人而获罪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.01,0:10:05.05,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,岂不是要我们妖精去死么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.68,0:10:08.85,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 快点去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.89,0:10:13.93,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,如果要怨的话 就去怨你们战败的祖先吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.10,0:10:17.65,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,迟早 你们精灵 矮人 霍比特人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.69,0:10:21.69,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这些亚人种族都会灭绝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.61,0:10:23.61,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.95,0:10:32.41,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你做什么！？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.54,0:10:35.96,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,间苗啊 拔掉多少人好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.29,0:10:39.46,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,上头说可以把人数减到一半呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.63,0:10:45.72,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.09,0:10:48.30,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,把我杀掉吧 杀我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.80,0:10:54.23,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 你还年轻 保重身体
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.23,0:10:58.90,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你还有作为一个微不足道的农奴的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.02,0:11:02.90,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不过帮助漂流物的你弟弟们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.98,0:11:05.95,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那些家伙就不行了 他们可是这件事的根源啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.28,0:11:12.79,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,现在应该已经变成尸体 沦为森林里虫子的食物了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.16,0:11:15.66,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,糟…糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.62,0:11:17.83,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.67,0:11:20.54,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,麦田着火了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.71,0:11:23.30,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什么！？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.42,0:11:26.22,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,现在可还没有收成啊 税收要减少了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.76,0:11:29.80,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明都那样提醒过了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.97,0:11:36.73,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,把麦田给点燃？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.10,0:11:37.89,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.48,0:11:42.23,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就算没有尊严 有饭可吃的话 人还可以活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.73,0:11:47.32,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,如果无饭可吃 却有尊严的话 人还能忍受过去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.07,0:11:51.95,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果两者都没有的话 就已经什么都无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.99,0:11:53.95,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他们就会不惜依靠任何力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.54,0:11:58.62,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是在一向一揆中吃足了这一伎俩中的苦头啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.54,0:11:58.62,Difters PS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(722.4,15)}一向一揆：日本战国时代净土真宗（一向宗）本愿寺派信徒所发起的起义之总称。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.08,0:12:02.13,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是拿下国家最好的一招
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.38,0:12:05.13,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真是可怕的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.09,0:12:10.97,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,果然火就是好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.97,0:12:14.76,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这让我回想起伊势长岛那次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.97,0:12:14.76,Difters PS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(924,15)}注：信长在长岛一向一揆中，将屋长岛、中江2城用几重的栅栏包围，放火烧城。城中2万余男女被烧死。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.36,0:12:28.61,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,麦田…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.11,0:12:32.07,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,干瞪着眼干什么 快去灭火
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.24,0:12:36.12,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,扩散到这么大范围已经没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.00,0:12:39.25,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.80,0:12:50.13,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,漂流物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.93,0:13:00.39,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,第一个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.77,0:13:05.98,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.61,0:13:09.69,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.82,0:13:11.61,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.87,0:13:18.37,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,第二个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.37,0:13:21.58,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,第三个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.96,0:13:26.00,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不能退缩 谁逃谁死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.63,0:13:30.71,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,第四个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.64,0:13:40.22,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,将领头目
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.35,0:13:43.35,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,将领头目
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.02,0:13:47.40,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,留下你的人头
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.48,0:13:50.61,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是这里的将领头目对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.57,0:13:57.03,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是漂流物吗 到底在说些什么鸟语
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.62,0:14:01.50,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是…漂流者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.58,0:14:06.08,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.25,0:14:09.92,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,马夏 马尔克 你们还活着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.67,0:14:14.84,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 是那个可怕的人救了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.97,0:14:16.72,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那个漂流者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.26,0:14:22.02,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么一回事…漂流者又到底是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.81,0:14:25.73,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,漂流物 竟敢妨碍我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.24,0:14:39.53,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,竟敢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.49,0:14:42.83,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,竟敢对他们下手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.58,0:14:51.04,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要你的人头了 我只要你的狗命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.88,0:14:54.30,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我不懂你在说些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.80,0:15:00.68,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,连说话都不会的野蛮人就让我们用剑来交流吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.01,0:15:02.85,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,漂流物 放马过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.02,0:15:06.39,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,阿拉姆他和其他的士兵可不一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.56,0:15:09.61,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他可是有代理官职的真正的骑士武官
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.69,0:15:12.94,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,即使是漂流者也…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.45,0:15:21.28,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,耍小聪明 走投无路了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.28,0:15:22.53,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,太轻松了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.14,0:15:42.68,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,没意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.09,0:16:17.67,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,利用刀鞘 行使组手甲胄术
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.05,0:16:19.80,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真是无情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.09,0:16:23.68,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 真吓人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.47,0:16:25.89,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,完事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.60,0:16:31.69,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 逃走的敌人已经一个不剩了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.98,0:16:37.36,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙真可怕 而你也很可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.44,0:16:43.32,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来 那家伙想要怎么做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.00,0:16:53.33,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.36,0:17:24.11,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,杀掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.71,0:17:32.58,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,杀掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.92,0:17:37.00,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你说不干？必须要下手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.13,0:17:40.09,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,必须要下手 不可以不杀掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.38,0:17:43.38,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不管这里是哪里你们又是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.55,0:17:46.14,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这个仇必须由你们来报
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.68,0:17:49.26,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这孩子正向你喊着帮我报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.56,0:17:57.23,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然语言不通 但心里却很清楚他在说些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.48,0:18:00.15,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真有你的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.30,0:18:31.89,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你们 住…住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.97,0:18:33.77,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 住手 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.06,0:18:37.65,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你们知道你们这样做会有什么后果吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.02,0:18:41.07,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我错了 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.11,0:18:43.90,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,救…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.59,0:19:03.67,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.38,0:19:05.59,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.01,0:19:10.85,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在都干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.93,0:19:12.60,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是伤患刚好的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.68,0:19:14.64,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 干了许多事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.89,0:19:16.27,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,许多事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.89,0:19:20.48,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,比起这些 你应该累了吧 你先坐下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.77,0:19:25.07,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,本来是我想坐的 不过还是让给你坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.45,0:19:31.16,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,大事不好了 大事不好了 他们居然…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.28,0:19:36.04,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,大师傅 他们 他们…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.39,0:19:53.51,Drifters Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(254.4,275.4)\frx340\fry16}岛津丰久
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.39,0:19:53.51,Drifters Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(866.4,297)\frx344\fry22}夺取精灵的村庄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.57,0:20:08.99,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你还在那里做着无用功的挣扎啊 紫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.53,0:20:15.83,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不管你多努力 还有不管你送去多少的漂流物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.45,0:20:19.00,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,最后的赢家都会是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.88,0:20:26.59,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不管你付出多少努力都是没有用的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.80,0:20:28.22,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你滚吧 EASY
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.76,0:20:31.13,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,扭曲的地方必须被矫正
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.97,0:20:36.60,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你滚吧 EASY
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.68,0:20:38.64,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不会如你所愿的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.48,0:20:43.10,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,可怜的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.02,0:20:47.07,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,可怜的是你才对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.78,0:20:50.40,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,能做到的话就做给我看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.12,0:21:01.50,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你的漂流物是不可能战胜我的废弃物的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.25,0:21:06.25,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是赛姆 这里是赛姆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.50,0:21:10.09,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,大师傅 他们居然夺得了那个村庄
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.22,0:21:12.38,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,在放任下去实在是太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.55,0:21:14.34,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在就把他们带到你那边去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.51,0:21:18.35,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 赶不上了 不能带过来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.60,0:21:20.14,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你也不要过来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.68,0:21:22.35,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那应该…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.69,0:21:24.90,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.83,0:21:38.70,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,已经开始了
